---
title: Smoky Pork Rice Bowls with Coleslaw, Pickled Shallot & Sweet Chili BBQ Sauce
description: You’ve had burrito bowls, salad bowls, grain bowls—but have you ever had a BBQ bowl? That’s right, folks—it’s backyard BBQ flavor, made weeknight-friendly thanks to paprika-spiced pork, creamy coleslaw, and speedy microwavable rice. It’s all piled together, topped with tangy pickled shallot, and drizzled with a chili BBQ sauce for a spicy-sweet finish. Build your own bowl for a customizable cookout-style dinner in just 20 minutes!
